name: Create a 1/1 every day for a year: Two artists with very different styles collaborate on a 1/1 piece fusing both their styl
description:
NikeJerk created the OG collage a week ago, using a variety for digital components and methods. TransientOddity happened to buy NJs work and became fixated on derivitizing it as part of his ongoing NeuralPython experimental projects…. The neuralnetwork and Python algo rebited the OG artwork, the AI under attentive guidance applied an alternative palette, textures and geometric details, as see here. 

This collab is limited to 6 editions only. 

https://hicetnunc.art/nikejerk

https://hicetnunc.art/transient_oddity
